# Subagent model — Grok

When launching **Task** subagents (Coach, Researcher, Strategist, Editor, explore, generalPurpose, shell, etc.), set:

```
model: grok-4.5-fast-xhigh
```

**Default for this repo (Dale 2026-07-12).** Do not use Claude / GPT / Composer for subagents unless Dale explicitly names a different model for that run.

Parent agent may stay on whatever model the chat is using; this rule is for **Task tool** `model` only.
